
<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Jogoo - Menu</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body class="theme-dark">
  <header class="topbar">
    <h1>Jogoo</h1>
    <nav>
      <button onclick="location.href='login.html'">Login / Cadastro</button>
      <button onclick="openChat()">Chat</button>
      <button onclick="location.href='perfil.html'">Perfil</button>
      <button onclick="location.href='admin.html'">Admin</button>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h2>Bem-vindo ao protótipo melhorado</h2>
      <p>Use o menu acima para navegar. O chat abre como modal.</p>
      <p>Se quiser voltar pro jogo, abra <code>orig_index.html</code> (versão original) ou integre o player ao novo menu.</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Chat modal -->
  <div id="chatModal" class="modal" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <header class="modal-header">
        <h3>Chat Global</h3>
        <button class="close" onclick="closeChat()">×</button>
      </header>
      <section id="chatArea" class="chat-area">
        <div id="messages"></div>
      </section>
      <footer class="modal-footer">
        <input id="msgInput" placeholder="Escreva uma mensagem..." />
        <button onclick="sendMessage()">Enviar</button>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="firebase.js"></script>
  <script src="chat.js"></script>
  <script>
  function openChat(){ document.getElementById('chatModal').style.display='flex'; }
  function closeChat(){ document.getElementById('chatModal').style.display='none'; }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
